"title": "5548: speech, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5548: speech, divine",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture assumes and affirms that God has spoken to many different people throughout the ages in a variety of ways.</p>\n<h2>Speech as a synonym for revelation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:1\">1SA 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:7\">1SA 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:19\">PSA 147:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6-John17:8\">JHN 17:6–17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:6-1Cor2:10\">1CO 2:6–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Different modes of divine speech</h2>\n<h3>The voice of nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:30-Isa30:31\">ISA 30:30–30:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3-Ps29:9\">PSA 29:3–29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:1-Job37:5\">JOB 37:1–37:5</a> <em>God's voice is depicted as thunder, the most awesome sound in nature</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:3\">ISA 33:3</a></p>\n<h3>A literal, audible voice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:34\">LUK 9:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:9-1Kgs19:13\">1KI 19:9–19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:31\">DAN 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:28-John12:29\">JHN 12:28–12:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3-Acts9:7\">ACT 9:3–9:7</a></p>\n<h3>Visions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen46:2\">GEN 46:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:8-Isa6:13\">ISA 6:8–6:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:11-Jer1:14\">JER 1:11–1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28-Ezek2:1\">EZK 1:28–2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:10\">ACT 18:9–18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:17-Acts22:18\">ACT 22:17–22:18</a></p>\n<h3>Dreams</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:24\">GEN 31:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:3-Gen20:7\">GEN 20:3–20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:5-1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:5–3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:15-Job33:18\">JOB 33:15–33:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20-Matt1:21\">MAT 1:20–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:19-Matt1:20\">MAT 1:19–1:20</a></p>\n<h2>Divine speech through human messengers</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10\">JHN 14:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:16\">JHN 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:28\">JHN 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:49-John12:50\">JHN 12:49–12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:24\">JHN 14:24</a></p>\n<h3>Prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:7-1Sam8:9\">1SA 8:7–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15\">2CH 36:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:4-Isa38:8\">ISA 38:4–38:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:10-Ezek3:11\">EZK 3:10–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:4-Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:4–7:12</a></p>\n<h3>Apostles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13\">1TH 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:11-Gal1:12\">GAL 1:11–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:2\">2PE 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:3\">1JN 1:1–1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Divine speech through angels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">ACT 8:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:20-Dan9:23\">DAN 9:20–9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:11-Luke1:20\">LUK 1:11–1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:26-Luke1:38\">LUK 1:26–1:38</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of divine communication</h2>\n<h3>Dialogues between individuals and God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:9-Gen4:15\">GEN 4:9–4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:16-Gen18:33\">GEN 18:16–18:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:3-Exod4:17\">EXO 3:3–4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:16\">ACT 9:10–9:16</a></p>\n<h3>Messages received by people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:1\">GEN 35:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">GEN 12:1–12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:1-Josh1:9\">JOS 1:1–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:4-2Sam7:16\">2SA 7:4–7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:11-1Kgs6:13\">1KI 6:11–6:13</a></p>\n<h2>Descriptions of divine speech</h2>\n<h3>The sound of God's voice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:1-Ezek43:2\">EZK 43:1–43:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:12\">1KI 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:15\">REV 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>The effect of God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:29\">JER 23:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:13\">ZEC 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:12\">HEB 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:15\">REV 19:15</a></p>\n<h3>The character of divine speech</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:6\">PSA 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30\">PSA 18:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:7–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:89\">PSA 119:89</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:160\">PSA 119:160</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:24-1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:24–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:8\">ISA 40:6–40:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's word is recognised and loved by his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:103\">PSA 119:103</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:1-Ezek3:3\">EZK 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:3-John10:5\">JHN 10:3–10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:48\">ACT 13:48</a></p>\n<h2>God's word is supremely revealed in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a></p>",
